      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="使用ssh-keygen创建公钥和密钥"><a href="#使用ssh-keygen创建公钥和密钥" class="headerlink" title="使用ssh-keygen创建公钥和密钥"></a>使用ssh-keygen创建公钥和密钥</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">按指令操作</span></div><div class="line"> ssh-keygen -t  rsa</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="使用ssh-copy-id把公钥复制到远程主机上"><a href="#使用ssh-copy-id把公钥复制到远程主机上" class="headerlink" title="使用ssh-copy-id把公钥复制到远程主机上"></a>使用ssh-copy-id把公钥复制到远程主机上</h2><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">#替换公钥名称以及远程服务器地址</div><div class="line">ssh-copy-id -<span class="selector-tag">i</span> ~/.ssh/id_rsa<span class="selector-class">.pub</span>  root@xxx<span class="selector-class">.xxx</span><span class="selector-class">.xxx</span><span class="selector-class">.xxx</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="最后就可以登录了"><a href="#最后就可以登录了" class="headerlink" title="最后就可以登录了"></a>最后就可以登录了</h2><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="selector-tag">ssh</span> <span class="selector-tag">root</span>@<span class="keyword">xxx</span>.<span class="keyword">xxx</span>.<span class="keyword">xxx</span>.<span class="keyword">xxx</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
